2008lo muMbayiloni wAjmahal hotal, oVbeVrA wrideVMtlapE jarigina muRkarula xAdi saMxarBaMlo kUdA ixe viXamEna mIdiyA awyuwsAhaM apAranaRtaM weVcciMxi.
oVkavEpu ugravAxulu wAjmahal hotallo uMdi, xAdulaku pAlpaduwuMte eVlraktAnik mIdiyA A xqSyAlanu prawyakRa prasAraM cesiMxi.
polIsulu wIsukuMtunna caryalu kUdA I saMxarBaMgA mIdiyA veVlladi ceyadaMwo kasab bqMxaM eVppatikappudu vyUhAlu mArcukuMtU BaxrawA xalYAlanu muppawippalu peVttiMxi.
