islAmik stet AP irAk aMd siriyA(EeVsEeVs) kIlaka nAyakudu, A ugravAxa saMsWa yuxXa maMwri oVmar al RisAnIni aMwamoVMxiMcinatlu ameVrikA eVMwo garvaMgA prakatiMcina 24 gaMtallo -1
irAkloni mosul nagarAniki xakRiNaMgA Karayaw pattaNaM samIpaMlo jarigina vEmAnika xAdullo oVmar maraNiMcinatlu ameVrikA rakRaNa SAKa kAryAlayaM peVMtagAn prakatiMciMxi.
I maraNaM XqvIkaraNa jarigina warvAwa islAmik stet ugravAxulu oVkiMwa XEryaM kolpowAremonane aMcanA uMxi.
ayiwe xIniki prawIkAraMgAnA annatlu PrAnslo awyaMwa kirAwakaMgA trakku xAdi jarigiMxi.
84 maMxi amAyakula prANAlu wIsina I koVwwa warahA ugraxAdi mareVnno praSnalanu rekeVwwiswunnaxi.
bahiraMga praxeSAlu, reVstAreVMtlu, prArXanA maMxirAlu ilA oVkkatemiti anni praxeSAllo ugravAxula xAdulu jaruguwUne unnAyi.
prapaMca vyApwaMgA xAxApu anni xeSAlU ugravAxula cewilo naligipowUne unnAyi.
marI PrAnslo ayiwe ilAMti xAdulu itIvali kAlaMlo leVkkaku miMci jaruguwunnAyi.
2015 janavari 7va wexIna PrAnsloni vyaMgya ciwrAla vAra pawrika cArlI heVbdo kAryAlayaMpE islAmik stet ugravAxulu kAlpulu jaripi 12 maMxini hawamArcAru.
moVhamax pravakwapE vyaMgya ciwrAlanu pracuriMcadaM cArlI heVbdo cesina wappixaM.
axe edAxi navaMbarlo PrAns rAjaXAni pArislo ugravAxulu mAraNahomaM jaripAru.
pArisloni Aru prAMwAllo ugramUkalu I kirAwakAniki weVgabaddAyi.
I xAruNa mAraNakAMdalo moVwwaM 8 maMxi ugravAxulu pAlgoVnnAru.
iMxulo eduguru AwmAhuwiki pAlpadagA oVkarini polIsulu hawamArcAru.
ippudu I koVwwa warahA xAdi jarigiMxi.
PraMc prajalu wama Ekyawanu cAti ceVppeMxuku nirvahiMcukune jAwIya xinowsavaM- bAstil de.
eVMwo AnaMxaMgA PrAns moVwwaM saMbarAllo munigi unna samayaMlo ugravAxi oVkadu I trakkuxAdi jaripAdu.
bAstil de saMxarBaMgA nIs nagaraMlo sEnika kavAwu jaruguwuMxi.
reVMdu rojula I paMduga civari rojuna rAwri bANasaMcA kAlci mugiswAru.
bAstil delo BAgaMgA bANAsaMcAnu vIkRiswunna samayaMlone trakku aXika vegaMgA pAxacArula vaMweVnapE nuMci prajalapEki xUsukeVlYliMxi.
BaxrawAxalYAlu kAlpulu jaripinA A trakku Agalexu.
trakku nuMci ugravAxi kAlpulu kUdA jaripAdu.
oVkka ugravAxi sqRtiMcina kalakalaMwo A prAMwamaMwA mqwaxehAlu ceVllAceVxarugA padi BayAnaka vAwAvaraNaM neVlakoVMxi.
krEswavulu eVkkuvagA unna xeSamEnA lOkika rAjyaMgA BAsilluwunna PrAnslo 2003 nuMci musliMla janABA peVrigipowU vacciMxi.
e mawAniki ceVMxina vArEnA kUdA A mawAniki ceVMxina vArugA weVlipe xuswulu vesukorAxani catta savaraNa cesukuni marI PrAns pAlakulu sarvamawa samAnawvAnni pAtiswunnAru.
roman kAWaliklu eVkkuvagA uMde PrAnslo e mawAniki ceVMxani vArugA 28 SAwaM maMxi prakatiMcukunnAru.
musliMlawo bAtu sikkulu, yUxulu kUdA eVkkuva saMKyalone unnAru kAnI musliMlu waracU wama mawAnni weVlipe xuswulu vesukovadaM lexA wama mawAniki ceVMxina jeVMdAlanu eVguraveyadaM xvArA akkadi praBuwvAniki cIkAkulu weVppiswunnAru.
60 lakRala maMxi aMte janABAlo 10 SAwaM maMxi musliMlu akkada nivaSiswunnArani aXikArika leVkkalu ceVbuwunnAyi.
akkadi mawaCAMxasa BAvAlanu reVccagoVttadAniki eVppudU oVka vargaM sixXaMgA uMdexi.
praSAMwamEna lOkika xeSaMlo waracU mawaM ciccu peVduwUne uMxi.
cArlI heVbdo pawrika kAryAlayaMpE xAdi jariginapudu reVMdo roju akkadi masIxulapE sWAnikulu prawixAdulu jaripAru.
appati nuMci akkada mawaM maMduwUne uMxi.
nIs nagaraMlo kUdA musliM janABA eVkkuva.
akkada eVMwo maMxi iwara xeSAlaku ceVMxina musliMlu ASrayaM poVMxuwuMtArata.
nIs nagaraM nuMci islAmik stet wIvravAxullo kalisevAru eVkkuvagA uMtunnAru.
aMte islAmik stet ugravAxa saMsWaku awyaXikaMgA rikrUtmeVMt jaruguwunnaxi nIs nagaraM nuMce.
1789 viplavaMwo prapaMcAniki svecCA, samAnawvaM, sOBrAwqwvAlanu prapaMca prajAsvAmyAniki iccina PrAns xeSaMlo paxepaxe ugravAxa xAdulu jaruguwUne uMdataM vicArakaraM.
PreVMc viplavaM AraMBamEna reVMdu rojulaku bAstil de jarupukuMtAru.
iMwati paviwraxinaM nAdu ugravAxulu I viXaMgA weVgabaddAru.
irAk, siriyA waxiwara xeSAllo ameVrikA newqwvaMlo jaruguwunna ugravAxa vyawireka xAdullo PrAns xalYAlu pAlgoVMtunnAyi.
PrAns xalYAlu ceswunna pani valla cAlA varaku ugravAxula SibirAlu wudicipeVttukupowunnAyi.
xIMwo PrAns islAmik stet ugravAxula lakRyaMgA mAriMxi.
islAmikstetlo cereMxuku EropA nuMci aneka maMxi yuvawa veVlYlAru.
maro vEpu vaMxalAxi musliM yuvakulu PrAns nuMci irAk, siriyAlaku waraliveVlYlinatlu niGAvargAlu heVccariswU vaccAyi.
vIraMwA jihAx sAXiMce lakRyaMwo EeVsEeVsku sAyapadeMxuku veVlYlArani kUdA PrAns praBuwvAniki weVlusu.
vIrilo PrAns nuMci veVlYlinavArixe kIlakapAwra.
ayiwe viviXa kAraNAlawo irAk, siriyA xeSAllo ugravAxa kAryakalApAllo pAlgoVnna aneka maMxi yuvakulu wirigi PrAnsku vacceSAru.
vIraMwA nijaMgA ugravAxAnni vidanAdArA leka iMkA slIparseVlsgA pani ceswunnArA anexi weVliyaxu.
A samayaMlo alKExA ugravAxulu PrAnslo eduguru vyakwulni nilabeVtti kAlcesi PrAnslo saMcalanaM sqRtiMcAru.
2012 nuMci alKExA ugravAxulu wama kAryakalApAlanu PrAnslo eVkkuva ceSAru.
oVkka PrAnslone kAxu anni EropA xeSAllo ixe viXamEna xAdulu jaruguwAyani EeVsEeVs ippatike heVccariMciMxi.
koVnni saMxarBAllo ugravAxa xAdi sqRtiMcina bIBawsaM kaMte, anusariMcina viXAnaM eVkkuva BayapeVduwuMxi.
PrAnsloni nEs nagaraMlo guruvAraM rAwri bAstil de saMbarAla kosaM gumigUdina vaMxalAxi maMxini oVka BArI trakkuwo woVkkiMci caMpeyAlanna Alocana oVka mAraNAyuXa xAdikaMte peVnuviRAxAnni migalciMxi.
I mqwyuSakataM kiMxa naligipoyi prANAlu kolpoyinavAru praswuwAniki vaMxalopu uMdavaccunemo kAnI, wIvraMgA gAyapadinavAri saMKya heVccugA unnaMxuna maraNAlu mariMwa peVruguwAyi.
bANAsaMcA vedukalanu cUddAniki aXikasaMKyalo pillalu kUdA vaccinaMxuna mqwullo paximaMxikipEgA vAre uMdataM manasunu piMdiveswunnaxi.
trakkulo mAraNAyuXAlu, peludupaxArWAlu kUdA unnAyani sWAnika mIdiyA aMtunnaxi.
axe nijamEna pakRaMlo vyUhaM mariMwa BayaMkaramEnaxani BAviMcAli.
xAdilo BAgaMgA vAtini kUdA upayogiMce Alocana unnA, avakASaM, samayaM cikkivuMdakapovaccu.
lexA, I BArI mqwyuSakatAnni vegaMgA parugulu wIyiMci eVkkuvamaMxini woVkkiMci caMpeyAlanna vyUhaM AcaraNa sAXyaMkAni pakRaMlone vAtini bayatakuwIyAlani anukoVni uMdavaccu.
kAnI, mAraNAyuXAlawo nimiwwaM lekuMdAne anukunnaxi sAXiMcagaligAdu A xurmArgudu.
vIkRakulu bArulu wIrina praxeSAniki vaMxa mItarla muMxu oVkkasArigA vegaM puMjukoVni, reVMdu kilomItarla varakU axi xUsukurAgalagadame AScaryaM kaligiMce sanniveSaM.
trakku veVMbadi parugulu wIswunna polIsulakU, drEvarku maXya parasparaM kAlpulu jarigAyi wappa, trakkunu wakRaName ApalekapovadaM vEPalyaMgAne kanipiswunnaxi.
I kAraNaMgAne axi prayANiMcina xAraMwA SavAlu pogubaddAyi.
e ugravAxa saMsWA I xAdiki bAXyawa prakatiMcakapoyinA, xInini ugravAxa xAdigA, iMxuku PrAnslo nivasiswunna tyunIRiyan musliM kArakudani PrAns praBuwvaM ippatike prakatiMciMxi.
prANAlaku weVgiMcina pakRaMlo, mAraNAyuXAlawo panilekuMdA, oVka vyakwi eVMwati viXvaMsAnikEnA pAlpadagaladani nEs Gatana nirUpiMciMxi.
eVMwati awyAXunikamEna niGAvyavasWalunnA koVMxaru vyakwulu saMkalpiMce ituvaMti bIBawsAlanu muMxugAne pasigattadaM, nivAriMcadaM kaRtamani kUdA welipowunnaxi.
mIku elA kuxiriwe alA... AyuXaMgA exi woswe axi aMtU islAmik stet iswunna saMxeSAlanu burrakeVkkiMcukunna vyakwulu eVtuvaMti vinUwnamEna Alocanalawo, e xArina virucukupadawArannaxi BayapeVduwunna aMSaM.
